description:
Some tracks that i liked from the Boozedrome VII (2024) event.
Art "Fury In Fur" by Folcka/Depth, 1st at Black Valley 2024 pixeled gfx compo.

00:00 Break - We Need Amigacore (1st)
02:58 Man With No Jumalauta Handle - Got Hardcore? (2nd)
05:47 Teo - King Of Bass (8th)
08:36 Triace - Break Ya Back (11th)

This upload has Brainworx VST effects and uses custom panning.

https://boozedrome.com/
https://boozedrome.bandcamp.com/album/boozedrome-vii-the-last-laugh

Made using real A1200 Rev. 1D.4 audio.

Visit my channel for more Amiga music.
title: Amiga music: Boozedrome VII picks (A1200🎧bx_)
